title: Grateful Dead Live at Winterland Arena on 1972-12-10
description:
Set 1

Cold Rain And Snow, Beat It On Down The Line, Don't Ease Me In, Black Throated Wind, Bird Song, El Paso, Around And Around, Tennessee Jed, Big River, Box Of Rain, Candyman, Bertha, Playing In The Band, Casey Jones

Set 2

The Promised Land, Stella Blue, Jack Straw, China Cat Sunflower > I Know You Rider, Truckin' > The Other One, Deal, Sugar Magnolia, Ramble On Rose, Johnny B. Goode, E: Uncle John's Band

reviews.review_text: - The jam in Other One is one of the coolest I've heard from the early 70s. Great Playin' too. It might be incomplete, but it cuts to the chase.
